# Student Management System

A comprehensive College Website built using Django that streamlines various academic and administrative tasks typically performed in a college environment. This web application is designed to simplify and digitize student and faculty management processes, offering a user-friendly interface for effective management.

# Features

Student Management:

Add, update, and delete student records.
View academic and personal details.
Faculty Management:

Manage faculty profiles and update their details.
Track subjects assigned to each faculty member.
Course and Subject Management:

Add and organize courses and subjects.
Assign subjects to specific faculty members.
Event Management:

Organize and track college events and sports activities.
Attendance Tracking:

Record and analyze student attendance.
Performance Monitoring:

Manage and evaluate student performance through marks and grades.

# Tech Stack
Backend: Django
Frontend: HTML, CSS, 
Database: Mongo DB SQLite 